<lb n="0542c12"/><head>No. 739</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0542c13"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0542020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0542020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0542020"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>慢法經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0542c14"/>
<lb n="0542c15"/><byline type="Translator">西晉<note n="0542021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">沙門＝三藏釋【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">沙門＝三藏釋【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542021"><lem>沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">三藏釋</rdg></app>法炬譯</byline>
<lb n="0542c16"/><p>佛<note n="0542022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">告＝語【三】，說【宮】</note><note n="0542022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">告＝語【宋】【元】【明】，＝說【宮】</note><app n="0542022"><lem>告</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">語</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>阿難。有人事佛<note n="0542023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以後便富貴＝已便有富貴不衰者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以後便富貴＝已便有富貴不衰者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542023"><lem>以後便富貴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已便有富貴不衰者</rdg></app>有人事
<lb n="0542c17"/>佛<note n="0542024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542024"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>後衰喪不利者。阿難<note n="0542025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（驚）＋問【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（驚）＋問【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542025"><lem>問</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">驚問</rdg></app>佛。云何俱事
<lb n="0542c18"/>佛。衰利不同。何故得爾。佛語阿難。有人事
<lb n="0542c19"/>佛。當求明師。得了了者。從受戒法。為除諸
<lb n="0542c20"/>想。與經相應。精進奉行。不失<note n="0542026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">其＝法【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">其＝法【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542026"><lem>其</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">法</rdg></app>教受者。不
<lb n="0542c21"/>犯如毛髮者。是人不犯道禁。常為諸天善神。
<lb n="0542c22"/><note n="0542027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（所）＋侍【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（所）＋侍【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542027"><lem>侍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">所侍</rdg></app>衛擁護。所向諧偶。財利百倍。眾人所敬。
<lb n="0542c23"/>後當得佛。何況富<note n="0542028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">利＋（耶）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利＋（耶）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542028"><lem>利</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">利耶</rdg></app>。如是人輩。事佛為真
<lb n="0542c24"/>佛弟<note n="0542029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">子＋（也）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">子＋（也）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542029"><lem>子</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">子也</rdg></app>。又復有人事佛。不值明師。亦無經
<lb n="0542c25"/>像。<note n="0542030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又復不＝復無【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">又復不＝復無【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542030"><lem>又復不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復無</rdg></app>禮敬。不知不解。強<note n="0542031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">教＝效【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">教＝效【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542031"><lem>教</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">效</rdg></app>人受法戒。
<lb n="0542c26"/>無有至信。受戒之後。故復犯眾戒。心意<note n="0542032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蒙＝朦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蒙＝朦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542032"><lem>蒙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">朦</rdg></app>
<lb n="0542c27"/>冥。猶豫<note n="0542033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（亦）＋不【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（亦）＋不【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542033"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">亦不</rdg></app>肯讀經行道作福。乍信乍不信。
<lb n="0542c28"/>復不能念齋日燒香燃燈作禮。故復瞋恚<note n="0542034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嚾＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0542034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嚾＝喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0542034"><lem>嚾</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">喚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0542c29"/>呼罵詈。出入&CB00057;<note n="0542035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咀＝詛【明】</note><app n="0542035"><lem>咀</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">詛</rdg></app>。口初不合心。懷憎嫉。使
<pb ed="T" id="T17.0739.0543a" n="0543a"/>
<lb n="0543a01"/>人殺生。<note n="0543001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眼〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔眼〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543001"><lem>眼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>見經像。無有禮敬之心。若其有
<lb n="0543a02"/>經。趣掛著壁。或擲床席之上。或著故衣被弊
<lb n="0543a03"/>篋器中。或以妻子小兒不淨手弄之。&CB00195;熏屋
<lb n="0543a04"/>漏。不復瞻視。亦不燒香燃燈向之作禮。與
<lb n="0543a05"/><note n="0543002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">外＝凡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">外＝凡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543002"><lem>外</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">凡</rdg></app>經書無異。善神離之。惡鬼得其便。隨逐
<lb n="0543a06"/><note n="0543003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不置〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不置〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543003"><lem>不置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。因衰<note n="0543004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＝疾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病＝疾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543004"><lem>病</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">疾</rdg></app>之。適得疾病。恐怖猶豫。自念
<lb n="0543a07"/>言。我初事佛。云何故復疾病<note n="0543005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝耶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543005"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>。不能自信。
<lb n="0543a08"/>呼使<note n="0543006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至醫師醫＝巫媚之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至醫師醫＝巫媚之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543006"><lem>至醫師醫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">巫媚之</rdg></app>師卜問。解除鎮厭無益。遂便
<lb n="0543a09"/>禱賽邪神。眾過遂增。妖魅惡鬼。屯守其門。遂
<lb n="0543a10"/>便喪衰死亡。不離門戶。財產衰耗。家室病
<lb n="0543a11"/>疾。更相注續。不離床席。命終<note n="0543007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔罪辜〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔罪辜〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543007"><lem>罪辜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。墮&CB00410;犁
<lb n="0543a12"/>中。當被考治&CB00353;罰。無有歲數。是人但坐不能
<lb n="0543a13"/>專一。志意猶豫。無所專據。不信佛法。故得其
<lb n="0543a14"/>罪<note n="0543008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殃＝凶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殃＝凶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543008"><lem>殃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">凶</rdg></app>。衰<note n="0543009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔耗〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔耗〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543009"><lem>耗</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>如是。世間人不知佛法者。謂呼
<lb n="0543a15"/>事佛令得殃衰。不知其人行自不正。違犯佛
<lb n="0543a16"/>經戒。心<note n="0543010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">專行惡＝意【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">專行惡＝意【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543010"><lem>專行惡</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>。眾態具足。身自招之。無有
<lb n="0543a17"/>與者。阿難聞之。<note n="0543011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便頭面＝便更頭腦【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">便頭面＝便更頭腦【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543011"><lem>便頭面</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便更頭腦</rdg></app>著地。為佛作禮。<note n="0543012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔歡喜奉行〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0543012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔歡喜奉行〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0543012"><lem>歡
<lb n="0543a18"/>喜奉行</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></p>
